msgstr "Choisir le canal de livraison"

msgid "Target Date Field"
msgstr "Champ de date cible"

msgid ""
"The date field on the record to schedule around (e.g., 'close_date', "
"'due_date'). Required for scheduled automations."
msgstr ""
"Le champ de date sur l'enregistrement autour duquel planifier (ex. : "
"'close_date', 'due_date'). Requis pour les automatisations planifiées."

msgid "Adjust By"
msgstr "Ajuster de"

msgid ""
"How many days/weeks/months away from the Target Date.\n"
"Use 0 to send on the same day."
msgstr ""
"Combien de jours/semaines/mois avant ou après la date cible.\n"
"Utilisez 0 pour envoyer le même jour."

msgid "Before"
msgstr "Avant"

msgid "After"
msgstr "Après"

msgid "Timing"
msgstr "Synchronisation"

msgid ""
"Before = send earlier than the Target Date.\n"
"After = send later than the Target Date."
msgstr ""
"Avant = envoyer avant la date cible.\n"
"Après = envoyer après la date cible."

msgid "Days"
msgstr "Jours"

